    ns1:otherInformation """Sessions will follow Flipped Classroom methodology
Students are encouraged in a Project to consider proposals that can accomplish with all SDG (Sustainable
Development Goals):
https://sdgs.un.org/es/goals
Students are encouraged to review Annual and Sustainability Reports all around the world."""@es ;
    ns1:periodEndingMonth "Enero"@es ;
    ns1:periodStartingMonth "Septiembre"@es ;
    ns1:teachingPeriod "2025-26" ;
    ns1:teachingPeriodMonths "Septiembre-Enero"@es ;
